If you wish to have this setting on, please mention so in your post. That way, people will know to add you to their contacts.

AdiversonHow many pupils I can invite every day??

You can have a maximum of 5 pupils in queue plus 2 in an active class.

You can send a maximum of 3 pupils a day. You can't send a pupil to anyone who's queue is full, or whom you already have a student in their queue (even if that queue is not full).

No, there is no way of knowing if a queue is full before sending, you only find out via the failure message when you try.
